title: Clinton says family paid State Dept employee for email work
text: Clinton says family paid State Dept employee for email work By Associated Press | September 5, 2015 @ 12:13 pm FILE - In this Aug. 26, 2015 file photo, Democratic presidential candidate Hillary Rodham Clinton speaks in Ankeny, Iowa. Clinton said Sept. 4, her use of a private email system at the State Department wasn't the "best choice" and acknowledged she didn't "stop and think" about her email set-up when she became President Barack Obama's secretary of state in 2009.(AP Photo/Charlie Neibergall, File)
